TITLE: Starting TigerBeetle Server
DESCRIPTION: Starts a TigerBeetle server instance listening on port 3000 in development mode.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tigerbeetle/tigerbeetle/blob/main/docs/start.md#2025-04-14_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: console
CODE:
```
