TITLE: Installing and Starting TigerBeetle Cluster on Linux
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to download TigerBeetle, format a data file, and start a single-replica cluster in development mode on Linux.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tigerbeetle/tigerbeetle/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-14_snippet_0

