TITLE: Creating and Voiding Pending Transfers in Java with TigerBeetle
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to create a pending transfer and then void it using the TigerBeetle Java client. It demonstrates the two-phase transfer process for creating and canceling a pending transfer.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tigerbeetle/tigerbeetle/blob/main/src/clients/java/README.md#2025-04-14_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
