TITLE: Creating a TigerBeetle Client in Go
DESCRIPTION: Code to initialize a TigerBeetle client with a cluster ID and replica addresses. The client is thread-safe and should be shared between concurrent tasks for optimal performance.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tigerbeetle/tigerbeetle/blob/main/src/clients/go/README.md#2025-04-14_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: go
