TITLE: Efficient Batched Transfer Creation in Go
DESCRIPTION: The recommended approach for creating transfers by batching multiple transfers in a single API call, up to the server's maximum batch size limit (default 8189), which significantly improves performance.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tigerbeetle/tigerbeetle/blob/main/src/clients/go/README.md#2025-04-14_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: go
CODE:
```
batch := []Transfer{}
BATCH_SIZE := 8189
for i := 0; i < len(batch); i += BATCH_SIZE {
	size := BATCH_SIZE
	if i+BATCH_SIZE > len(batch) {
		size = len(batch) - i
	}
	transferErrors, err := client.CreateTransfers(batch[i : i+size])
	_, _ = transferErrors, err // Error handling omitted.
}
```

