TITLE: Creating Accounts in TigerBeetle using Java
DESCRIPTION: Creates an account batch and adds a single account with specified properties. The account is given a unique time-based ID, ledger and code values, and flags that control account behavior. The batch is then submitted to TigerBeetle.
