TITLE: Efficient Batched Transfer Creation
DESCRIPTION: Best practice example for creating transfers in batches up to the server's maximum batch size (default 8189), greatly improving performance by reducing network roundtrips.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tigerbeetle/tigerbeetle/blob/main/src/clients/dotnet/README.md#2025-04-14_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: C#
