TITLE: Docker Authentication Setup
DESCRIPTION: Command to configure Docker authentication using a JSON key file for accessing the container registry.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tigerbeetle/tigerbeetle/blob/main/src/testing/systest/README.md#2025-04-14_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
cat /some/path/to/tigerbeetle.key.json | docker login -u _json_key https://us-central1-docker.pkg.dev/ --password-stdin
```

