TITLE: Explicit Parameter Passing in Zig Function Calls
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates explicitly specifying all options when calling library functions rather than relying on defaults, which improves code clarity and prevents bugs if library defaults change.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tigerbeetle/tigerbeetle/blob/main/docs/TIGER_STYLE.md#2025-04-14_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: zig
CODE:
```
@prefetch(a, .{ .cache = .data, .rw = .read, .locality = 3 });
```

